rComments: I took from him a course on Ukrainian politics. He gives readings, but class discussions may become irrelevant to class subject and readings. He speaks of US politics and Africa. If you are not American or have no idea about US politics, you just watch people talking about US politics for hours. He is probably a good academic but a horrible prof.
Arrogant! Do not recommend this prof!

Amazing! Super helpful and really cares about his students. Very enthusiastic about his own work and seems to like teaching. Likes to hear from students and will engage you in class debate so be ready. Unlike so many profs has a great sense of humour. :)
He's good at explaining things and is extremely enthusastic about everything!

he was pretty good - lots of work and a long final paper. keep up with work and you will leanr something. he is pretty nice and helpful - but don't question his core beliefs - he doesn't like that too much! overall, he was good and i would recommend him.
